item_category: The Fierce Voodoo is powered by an AMD Ryzen 5 3400G CPU that includes on-board Vega 11 graphics. This CPU combined with 8GB of Corsair RAM delivers fantastic performance for entry level gaming. Windows 10 Home is pre-installed on this system allowing you to plug and play right out of the box. Connect to your home network with ease as this gaming computer is Wi-Fi enabled.
